---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Shop Beat Namibia"
  description="Shop Beat Namibia — in-store audio and retail media for malls, supermarkets and retailers. Request a demo."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Shop Beat Namibia</h1>
      <p>In-store audio &amp; retail media for Namibia — malls, supermarkets and retailers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container page-content__inner">
      <img src="/assets/images/brands/shopbeat.png" alt="Shop Beat" style="width: 100%; max-height: 280px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 32px;" />

      <h2>What is Shop Beat?</h2>
      <p>Shop Beat is Future Media's dedicated retail media programme for Namibia. It is the only Namibian web home for Shop Beat — there is no redirect to a South African site. We help retailers and brands reach shoppers at the point of decision with in-store audio and retail media placements.</p>

      <h2>How it works</h2>
      <p>Retail advertisers get priority placement during peak shopping hours, promotional slots on retail-focused shows, and integration with Shop Beat channels that reach consumers actively looking for deals. Campaigns combine radio call-to-actions, digital promotions and in-store audio to drive foot traffic and sales.</p>

      <h2>Who it's for</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Retailers and supermarket groups</li>
        <li>Shopping malls and centre management</li>
        <li>FMCG and consumer brands with in-store goals</li>
        <li>Agencies planning retail / in-store campaigns</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Features &amp; benefits</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Flash sales</h3>
          <p>Same-day radio and digital promotion for time-sensitive retail offers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Mall activations</h3>
          <p>Live broadcasts and brand activations from major shopping centres.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Loyalty integration</h3>
          <p>Connect loyalty programmes with exclusive listener and shopper offers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Namibia-first</h2>
      <p>This page targets searches like “in-store audio Namibia”, “retail media Namibia” and “Shop Beat Namibia”. Content is written and managed on futuremedia.com.na for the local market.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 24px;">
        <a href="/contact?interest=shop-beat" class="btn-primary">Request a demo</a>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #5a6570; margin-top: 12px;">Demo requests are routed to shopbeatnam@futuremedia.com.na</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
